{
  "texts": [
    "You, hypothetical voter, gain from the mass deployment of AI opinion polls.",
    "They provide you with cues that are sufficiently diverse to enhance the quality of decisionmaking.",
    "They generate reliable information as to when to vote tactically and when it is preferable to vote for your actual preference.",
    "The increased granularity and frequency of AI polling is liable to enhance the quality of democratic choice.",
    "Given how electoral politics is a high-stakes game, this is a crucial development."
  ]
}